public class JdkMapAdapterStringMap extends Object implements org.apache.logging.log4j.util.StringMap

      for performance reasons since 2.23. Use JdkMapAdapterStringMap(Map, boolean) instead.

    • JdkMapAdapterStringMap

      public JdkMapAdapterStringMap(Map<String,String> map, boolean frozen)
      Constructs a new StringMap, based on a JDK map.

      The underlying map should not be modified after this call.

      If the Map implementation does not allow modifications, frozen should be set to true.

      Parameters:
      map - a JDK map,
      frozen - if true this collection will be immutable.
